{"tid":1652431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE HKDI自己同學 自己校園自已救","createTime":"2019-10-13T16:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T05:48:06.000Z","uid":146826,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"956d930fb6a8e625d7df07eca74add6edae04f17","tid":1652431,"uid":146826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zEfJ0X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEfJ0X4.jpg&h=9e324bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由呢場運動開始有第一個犠牲者開始就已經係輸咗<br />\n但係我地唔可以輸得更慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢件事人人有責</span></span><br />\n深知道各位同事都有要事要係學校處理<br />\n要上堂嘅要交功課嘅<br />\n都希望你地搞掂曬啲嘢之後會為公義企出嚟<br />\n街坊多謝你地一直幫拖<br />\n但係自己學校唔可以靠曬外人幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地IVE唔可以再做大專界孤兒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">促請校方公開真相<br />\n公開閉路電視片段<br />\n要幫陳同學沉冤得雪</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1f5f8cd79734fa0ab1c740de30466588757db33","tid":1652431,"uid":146826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"956d930fb6a8e625d7df07eca74add6edae04f17","tid":1652431,"uid":146826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zEfJ0X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEfJ0X4.jpg&h=9e324bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由呢場運動開始有第一個犠牲者開始就已經係輸咗<br />\n但係我地唔可以輸得更慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span 